quran[99]{c,v,t}:
  15,1,Alif-Laam-Raa (edde faxem Yalli yaaxige) amah Qhuraan kitaabih aayootaa kee baxxaqqa le Qhuraan kinni
  15,2,"koroosite mari Akeeral, addunyal muslimiinih sugaanam sinnik qaagitak yenen"
  15,3,Nabiyow ama koros addunyal takamay hataktay usun addunyah- lon baaker Yallih taaqatak ken gabxisay ixxic;toysa addunyaay akeeral ken geyuwaa finga sarrah Aaxige loonuk
  15,4,Magaaloolî marak hebeltô magaalah mara mafinqisinno tet mara edde finqisnaah bayisna waktiy finqah keenih xagne yani kaa akke waytek
  15,5,Hebeltoh ummattay finqi teetik edde yan waktik taakumeeh wadirrowta matan
  15,6,"Nabii Mucammad fraseo dirabboyse mari (koros kinnuk) anqasah kaak iyyeh : kee Qhuraan elle obsime numow diggah atu cabuli anu Nabii kinniyo itta waqdi"
  15,7,Malayka macah neh baahe waytaa Yalli nee fan koo ruubeemih koh sumaaqittamkeh atu numma yacee marih num tekkek? kaak iyyen
  15,8,"Yalli keenil gacisak iyyeh :Nanu malayka moobisna cakkķil finqa kah fanna marih digaalah ken oobisna nee akke waytek, toysa malayka ken digaalah obta waqdi usun wadirroysima mara hinnon"
  15,9,"Diggah Nabii Mucammadal Acsaei yo Qhuraan oobissem Nee, diggah kaa (Qhuraan kinnuk) dacrissam nee tu kaat ossaanaah tu kaak daggoysaanamak"
  15,10,Nummah Nabii Mucammadow Aae kok duma farmoytit rubneh naharsi ummattah buttaatil
  15,11,Ni farmoytiitik hebeltô farmoytay keenih yamaate mayan kaal anqasak sugeenim akke waytek
  15,12,Nabii Mucammadow ġcgaseńięe kok duma rubne farmoytit dirabboyse marih lubbittet koroosannu kah culusne innaah makki korosih umeyniitih lubbittet kaa culusnah
  15,13,"Nabii Mucammadow åĝcjaseiýgo ama koros koo kee kool oobisne Qhuraan ma nummassa, nummah koros finqisnam naharsi marih gitay tatrey Yalli ken finqah madqe kinni"
  15,14,Makki korosuh qaran afoofik afa fakinninoy tokkel malayka ubullu haanam fanah awaquk kaat asak yeneeniih woh nummaysak manannon
  15,15,Cagalah Ni intiita alfinteeh korteh wonna hinnay Nanu elle baaben mara kinnino axcuk yenen cirdih (Qinaadih)
  15,16,"nummah Ni dudda tascasse astootik tanim: addunyâ Qaraanal cutuukâ mafdagoogi hayneeh cutuukut kaa bilqisne kaa fan waktaah cubbusaah elle kaskassoowa marah"
  15,17,kulli sheytanay Yallih Racmattak xiiriyimek kaa (Qaran kinnuk) dacrisneh
  15,18,Sheytanay qaraanal tan malaykah yab ankacisaah hadfaah garqay hadiidiga dabiiti kataataah carrisa akke waytek
  15,19,"baaxo fidisneeh farakka tet hayneeh qaleelay diggi tet hayta teetil hayne, ummaan iimik timixxigeemiy caggudsumte teetil nuysubuke"
  15,20,"quusi siinih teetil (baaxo kinnuk) hayne, xayloo kee lacay tuxxiq edde litoonuy rizqhi kak siinil anee waa siinih ginne"
  15,21,"Gino tuxxiq edde leemik tu matan kadnoonî mafaatic Ni xaqul kak yanih akke waytek, Qaraanak baaxô fanah tet (Yallih kadnooni kinnuk) moobisna timixxigeemiy caggudsumte teetik oobisna nee akke waytek"
  15,22,"caacooyay qubulta lakabta (labakta) rubneeh Qaraanak robti lee oobisneeh tet sin nafqeeh, isin tet daanissaanam maduddan Nanu tet siinih daanisna nee akke waytek"
  15,23,diggah nanu naynuwweeh nanu qidnaah baaxoo kee baaxô bagul tanim inkih nanu nagra mara kinnino
  15,24,"nummah Nabii Aadamak xabba haanamaay tawayâ fan siinik rabtem Nanu neexegeh, nummah siinik nuwwam kee Qhiyaamah ayrô fanah tamaatu waytaamay wadirrowte Nanu Neexegeh"
  15,25,"diggah ku Rabbi Qhiyaamah ayro usuk ken gaaboyse le cisab kee galtoh, diggah usuk isi abtol naggaaraay ummaanim yaaxigi kinniih kaak qellittam matan"
  15,26,nummah seehadaytu (Nabii Aadam kinnuk) kafin kallay kanniy ittay dataah saanittek kaa ginne
  15,27,Jinni abbay jaan deqsita (ibliis kinnuk) kaxxa niqna le giray qer (qir) Aalle waytak kaa ginne Nabii Aadamak duma
  15,28,Nabiyow cus; ku Rabbi malaykak diggah Anu seehadaytu kafin kallay kanniy ittay dataah saanitteeh bisi kak milaggootek kaa gine kinniyo teetik iyye waqdi
  15,29,"Tokkel gino kaak missossuuy Yi xaquk yan rooci kaat fuufuyyu haa waqdi, toysa isin malaykak kaah kummaatak gomboh kaah rada massakaxxah"
  15,30,Tokkel malayka inkih kummatte num keenik cine kal
  15,31,Kinnih immay ibliis malaykâ luk Nabii Aadamah kummaata num yakkem cineh
  15,32,"Yalli ibliisik : kee ibliisow maca litoo?Malaykâ luk Aadamah kummaata num kah akke waytam kaak iyye"
  15,33,Ibliis kaxxa mariinoo kee kuuxe waynaanah anu seehadaytuy kafin kallay kanniy ittay dataah saanitteeh bisi kak milaggootek ginteh kummaatam yoo maceltaay maaba iyye
  15,34,"Yalli kaal gacisak : toysa jannatak eweq diggah atu yi Racmattak yexxeereeh xiiriyime num kinnitok kaak iyye"
  15,35,diggah cisab kee galtoh ayrô fanah Yi naqabuu kee Yi Racmattak taxxeerem kol tanayik
  15,36,Yi Rabbow addunyal yoo wadirros ku naqoosa edde ugussa ayrô fanah iyye ibliis
  15,37,"Yalli kaal gacisak :tokkel diggah atu ibliisow gino inkih edde rabtu wayta ayrô (Qhiyaamah ayro kinnuk) fanah raba kak wadirrosne marat tanto kaak iyye"
  15,38,Wakti kak yimixxige ayrô fanah sugetto (gino inkih edde rabta ayro kinnuk) kaak iyye
  15,39,Ibliis Yi Rabbow yoo makkosseeh makot yoo beyteemih sabbatah baaxô bagul Aadam Samadat ku amrî cina keenit bilqiseyyooh tirtô gitak inkih ken makkoyseyyooh ken maxqawiseyyo iyye
  15,40,Ku naqoosay tirri haytey isi qibaadah doorittey qibaada koh caglissa akke waytek
  15,41,"Yalli kaal gacisak : ah Yi gitay massooway yoo gudduysaah dacayri yol kak tani kinni kaak iyye"
  15,42,"Diggah atu Yi naqoosay qibaada yoh caglissa makkossaamih dudda ken amol mantu, kinnih immay atu makot beytaamih dudda kah litom makkoote maray koo kataate kaak iyye Yalli"
  15,43,diggah jahannam gira ibliis kee kaa kataate marak inkih xagni arac kinni
  15,44,"jahannam gira is malcina afa leeh malciin takke, kulli afa teetik ibliis kataate marak kulli mari keenik yimixxige kuray baxsime teetik le"
  15,45,Diggah Yalli maqaanek ken kah amrisem abaah usuk ken kak waaseemik yaxxeere mari jannootaa kee gexxa daroorih addal yan
  15,46,"Kulli umaanek nagaynan luk, kulli digaalák amaanah anuk tet (jannoota kinnuk) cula keenik iyyan"
  15,47,ken (moominiin kinnuk) lubbittek baguumaanee kee kuuxewaynan kalleh usun toobokoh anuk kacanu luk qaraakiy amol itta fan wagitak daffeyan jannat addal
  15,48,Usun tet (Jannoota kinnuk) addal taqabii kee Saqsaqitik tu ken elle maxagtaay usun teetik inkinnah yawqe mara hinnon
  15,49,"Nabiyow Yi naqoosah waris, diggah anu dambi cabti li xuwaw li kinniyom yol gace marah"
  15,50,Nabiyow diggah Yi digaala is qansarissa digaala kinnim keenih waris yol gacam cine marah
  15,51,"Nabii Mucammadow ġcsaseio Nabii Ibraahim qibinih (malayka Kinnuk) xaagu keenih waris, Yalli Nabii Ibraahim baxa geyuwaamih ayti kumaa kee Nabii Luut marih baysah ken ruube waqdi"
  15,52,"Malayka kaal culteeh salaamaqle kaal qidde waqdi salaąaamaqle keenih yukkuqeeh maaqo keenih xayyoyse, tokkel woo maaqo isik akmewaanam keenik yuble waqdi, diggah nanu siinik meesitnah keenik iyye"
  15,53,"Malayka Nabii Ibraahimik :ma meesitin diggah nanu kol kah nemeetem ixxiga le baxal koo ayti kumusnamkeh iyyaanama kaak itte"
  15,54,"Nabii Ibraahim qajjibsitak : idoolanni yoo kee yi barra inkih geek lakalaa isin baxal yoo aytikumussaanam ?Ah anninnah tan aytikumaay yoh abtaanam keenik iyye"
  15,55,"Malayka Ibraahimow nummah asmatleemiy raq sinnil koo ayti kumusnak, toysa atu nanu koo elle aytikumusnaamak yabboode marih num makkin kaak itte"
  15,56,Nabii Ibraahim isi Rabbih Racmatak iyyi yabboodee makkoote maray tirtô gitak makkoote akke waytek keenik iyye
  15,57,Yallih xaquk rubsumte malaykay isin yoo elle aytikumusseenimik kalah edde temeeten caagid siinik macaay keenik iyye
  15,58,Diggah Nanu umeyniitih yan marâ fanah rubsumne ken fingisnankeh kaak itte malayka
  15,59,Nabii Luutu kee kay buxah marak kaal teemenem kee keenik kalah kay marak kaal teemeneemiy nanu finqak inkih naggosnu wayna akke waytek
  15,60,Kinnih immay kay barray koroositte diggah is raqqa iyye marâ lih raqtam teetil mekelle digaalat
  15,61,Tokkel Yallih xaquk rubsumte malayka Nabii Luutul temeete waqdi
  15,62,Diggah isin waagisan mara kinnitoonuuh anu sin maaxigak maca faxxaanaa? keenik iyye Nabii Luut
  15,63,Wonna hinnay nanu Yallih farmoytiitik atu ma meesitin nanu digggah ku Rabbih xaquk ku mari edde agaywaagitak suge digaalá keenih luk kol nemeetek kaak (Nabii Luut kinnuk) iyyen
  15,64,"nanu Yallih xaquk numma luk kol nemeete, diggah nanu innaamat numma yacee mara kinnino kaak iyyen"
  15,65,"Toysa atu isi buxah maray yeemene luk barak tut edde kuulaay atu ken lakat gexaay ken katay, wadirih num waliqqi siinik hee waay, isin elle amrisinten kabû fanah warrayaay gexa kaak iyyen"
  15,66,"Nabii Luutul ama caagidih, diggah tama ku maray koroositek ellecabo finqaay saaxa, num keenik raaqe kalah maaci maacisa waqdi iyyaanamah wacyi kaal oobisne"
  15,67,Nabii Luut magaalah mari Nabii Luut xaqul qibni yanim yoobbe waqdi wallitak yemeeten umaane keenit abaanamkeh
  15,68,"Nabii Luut diggah A mari yi qibinaay Yi dacayrih gubat yaniinik, toysa isin yoo mayqunxinaay yoo ma wacarriysina keenik iyye"
  15,69,Yallih digaalak meesitaay umaaneh ken ma niyaatinaay yoo mayqunxiyina keenik iyye
  15,70,"Kay mari kaal gacisak : nanu koo mawaasinninoo? sinaamak hebeltô marih qibnaytiinok kaak iyyen"
  15,71,"Nabii Luut tamah Yi sayyok sinni caagid yagdubeeh abam faxa mara tekkeenik ken digbisita, Yalli caraamu abem maabina lab maral orobtaanamal keenik iyye"
  15,72,Nabii Mucammadow ġzsaeio ku-qumril xiibita immay diggah Nabii Luut mari usun gibdi maxqawitih (mako) addat yanin baditiiy agaywaagat amo ayxaaruk kaak iyye Yalli
  15,73,"Edde luk digaalâ xongoloy ken finqissa ken tibbixeeh keenil obte, ayro tawqe wakti"
  15,74,Tokkel ken magaaloolik (Nabii Luut marih magaalooli kinnuk) iro guba teetik ciggiilisneeh girat alasne kallah xeet robti innah irok keenil canne
  15,75,Diggah ken xagteeh keenil obte digaalat kasleeh cubbusa marah Yallih duddaa kee kay inkittinaane tascasse astooti edde tan
  15,76,diggah Nabii Luut marih magaalooli gitay safar mari kak tatrak addal tanik elle makaskassoowaanaa
  15,77,Diggah nanu keenit abne finqat yeemene marah baxxaqqa itta asta edde tan
  15,78,nummah maggo cooxuy gaabuh yani le magaaloolih mari (Nabii Shuqeybi mara kinnuk) usun sinni nafsi koroosannut yudlume marah sugen
  15,79,"Tokkel cane keenil gacisneeh ken bayisneh, ken dabooqa (Nabii Luut kee Nabii Shuqeybi marih dabooqa kinnuk) baxxaqqa iyya gitay sinam safarah kak gactal tanik usun elle makaskassoowaanaa"
  15,80,nummah Cijri deqsita daqaarih mari (Nabii Saalic mara kinnuk) farmoytit dirabboyseeh wohul Yallih farmoytit inkih dirabboyse mara yekken
  15,81,"Nabii Saalic marah Ni duddaa kee Nabii Saalic cakkil keenih yemeetem tascasse astooti (alaa kee wohuk kalah kaah necee astooti kinnuk) keenih necee, tokkel usun derre teetit cabeeniih teetil kaskassoowa mara makkon"
  15,82,"usun (Nabii Saalic mara kinnuk) qaleela urak (orak) Qarwa edde haysitak sugen, is keenil taddigilleemik amaanah anuk"
  15,83,Tokkel digaalâ xongoloy ken finqissa ken tibbixeeh maacay maacisa keenil obte
  15,84,Tokkel ken maaluu kee ken kalqootay qaleelat urak (orak) sugeeni keenih xiqtem mali Yallih digaalak
  15,85,"Qaranwaa kee baaxooy, ken nammayih fanal tanim cakkik sa elle ginnem mannu, diggah Qhiyaama edde ugutta wakti yamaatu waam raq mali, toysa Nabiyow atu qaxmeqe qafu keenih (koros kinnuk) abaay, usun kol baaheenim keenih cab"
  15,86,Diggah Nabiyow ku Rabbi ummaanim gineeh isi naqoosah caaloota yaaxigi kinni
  15,87,Nummah Nabiyow faatica deqsitta suuray malcina aayat takkey kulli salaatal gacam gacsimtaa kee nabah yan Qhuraan koh necee
  15,88,"Diggah Nabiyow addunyal ama korosuk garu edde hatkisne maaluy maggo afah yanî fanah isi namma inti sangeelih maruubin, usun Yallal aamine waanamah keenih marookitinaay, Yallaa kee kay farmoyta nummasse moominiinih nacrooraay, Ramma keenih ixxic"
  15,89,Diggah Nabii Mucammadow Jcsakeiķe anu Yallih amri cina mara Yallih digaalak meesiisey meesisso kak baxxaqqa itta kinniyo keenik ixxic
  15,90,Nabii Mucammadow åzsateiýço Qhuraan kol oobisneh yahuud kee nasaaral tawraat kee injiiliy usun tu kak nummayseeniih tu kak dirabboyseeni keenil kah oobisne innaah
  15,91,"Usun (Qhureyshi korosuuy, yahuud kee nasaarâ koros kinnuk) Qhuraan kura kurah hee mara kinnon, tu kaak nummaysaanaah tu kaak dirabboysaanamal"
  15,92,Tokkel Nabii Mucammadow ku Rabbi isil xiibitak nanu diggah Qhiyaamah ayró gino inkih esserenno iyye
  15,93,Usun addunyal numtinwwellitte qibaadaa kee wohuk kalah abak suggu iyyeenimil inkih
  15,94,"Toysa Nabii Mucammadow cakki seecoy ku Rabbi koo kah amrise fayyah, fayya hayisaay, korosut derre cabaay, ken umaanet tu mawin"
  15,95,Diggah Nabiyow nanu Qhureyshi korosih abbobtiy kol anqassah umaanek koo xiqneh ken bayisneemil
  15,96,"Yallâ luk aka Yalla haa mari, sinni uma taamah ellecabo sarrah Aaxigelon, Addunyaa kee akeeral"
  15,97,Nummah Nabiyow diggah atu usun kok iyyaanamat kaalil ceytam nanu naaxigeh
  15,98,"Toysa Nabii Mucammadow atu isi Rabbi saytunnoysak faylisaay, Yallah salat abaah kaa yaqbude marih num tik, koo biyaktaamak usuk koo xiqelek"
  15,99,Nabii Mucammadow isi Rabbi umman uqbud Rabi koh amma iyyam fanah kaak iyye Yalli